data.description: This property is a charming 2-story home situated in the desirable Ventana Subdivision, offering convenience to Fort Carson, shopping centers, dining options, and easy access to I25. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a well-maintained interior featuring a bright and open floor plan. The spacious living room seamlessly flows into the kitchen and dining area, providing a perfect space for gatherings and entertainment. The dining area conveniently walks out to the backyard, which boasts open space and stunning mountain views, creating a serene outdoor retreat. Heading upstairs, you'll find the master bedroom complete with a cozy sitting or dressing area, a luxurious 5-piece en-suite bath, and a generous walk-in closet. Additionally, there are two more bedrooms, a full bath, and a laundry area, offering comfort and convenience for everyday living. This home is move-in ready and sure to impress with its desirable location, functional layout, and picturesque views. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this gem your own—schedule a private showing today before it's gone!
